data.description: Motivated Seller!!! Welcome to your dream home in the highly desirable Highland Park neighborhood with no HOA! This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom property offers the perfect blend of comfort and style with captivating mountain views. Situated on a generous quarter-acre lot, with room to expand, this home boasts a range of modern updates and amenities that make it truly exceptional. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting living space flooded with natural light from the newer windows. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and kitchen, creating an ideal space for family gatherings and entertaining guests. Recent renovations include updated electrical, a new AC unit, a high-efficiency furnace, and a hot water heater and brand new windows, ensuring your comfort and peace of mind year-round. The primary suit offers a beautiful glass shower enclosure as well as a sunroom to take in the magnificent sunsets with your amazing view. This neighborhood as it all…walking distance to the future project of Broomfield town square, library, community center, bay aquatic park, parks and much more. Not to mention top rated Boulder Valley School.
